Ideally this map is supposed to be played under the conditions our server is set up with.

This map is one of several being designed for an attempt at a game mod we are working on but apparently its not different enough to warrant a category so it got landed in Knife Arena.

For optimum playability, try adjusting the gravity to 400, or if you want to try it on the server it was made for, go here:
